大鼻嘴細瘦臉 點樣唔靚？ 五官直情係完美啦<br />\n唔好駁我佢係整容 一睇返佢以前個樣就知佢係減肥減到咁 <br />\n當佢有整過 佢都整得好自然好靚 仍然係南泡第一仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X11YWpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX11YWpa.png&h=ddcb3acc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoJwwYd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoJwwYd.jpg&h=307ce4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDN9iCX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDN9iCX.gif&h=8c025039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7DWaNwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7DWaNwH.jpg&h=d1e11bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n確定不是實拍和修圖的差距嗎 不精修這臉能看嗎<br />\n是我瞎了還是你瞎了?你姐姐長不長這樣你心裡沒點數?別的美女找黑圖都是找素顏找崩圖，就你家姐姐黑圖是無修圖，不愧是南韓四代第一仙她的粉絲都這樣，閉上眼拿著一堆精修圖一堆疊了十層濾鏡的動圖在那裡狂吹，修圖的時候就修的媽都不認識，成天拉踩別家，你說真美女就算了，憑這個捏了臉還要疊八百層濾鏡然後站子精修一番都被一堆人不認可的你姐姐?口區<br />\n<br />\n作者：匿名用戶<br />\n鏈接：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/53248170/answer/611898160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F53248170%2Fanswer%2F611898160&d=vUt%2FZqt5lAJzOS14TgBfpw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=d04bb94b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/53248170/answer/611898160</a><br />\n來源：知乎<br />\n著作權歸作者所有。商業轉載請聯繫作者獲得授權，非商業轉載請註明出處。"},{"pid":"eca4d6a390216bd85f49ff29e5cd46c815dbeab4","tid":1097032,"uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"68fb45b57c0b6b4c380e1270384850a993110172","tid":1097032,"uid":1086,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"33e42b0588888fc08aab35b8883b60cd90b849f9","tid":1097032,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"同佢鬥到四代神顏就只有智秀一個 不服來駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyT